OL,3,CMan to appear in court after allegedly
OL,4,Cthreatening Andrew on Sandringham
OL,5,CEstate
OL,7,FA man will appear in court after being
OL,8,Fcharged with allegedly threatening
OL,9,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor near his
OL,10,Fnew home on the Sandringham Estate.
OL,12,FThe former Duke of York was out
OL,13,Fwalking his dogs when the incident
OL,14,Foccurred in Wolferton, close to his
OL,15,FMarsh Farm property, shortly after
OL,16,F7.30pm on Wednesday, the Telegraph
OL,17,Freported previously.
