OL,3,CMan to appear in court after allegedly
OL,4,Cthreatening Andrew on Sandringham
OL,5,CEstate
OL,7,FAlex Jenkinson, 39, of Stowmarket,
OL,8,FSuffolk, has been charged with two
OL,9,Fcounts of using threatening, abusive
OL,10,For insulting words or behaviour to
OL,11,Fharass someone or cause alarm or
OL,12,Fdistress, Norfolk Constabulary said on
OL,13,FThursday night.
OL,15,FHe has also been charged with failing
OL,16,Fto provide a specimen of blood in
OL,17,Fcustody and is due to appear at
OL,18,FNorwich Magistrates Court on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
