OL,3,CMan to appear in court after allegedly
OL,4,Cthreatening Andrew on Sandringham
OL,5,CEstate
OL,7,FThe former duke, who is eighth in line
OL,8,Fto the throne, was detained on his
OL,9,F66th birthday following allegations
OL,10,Fthat he shared reports of official
OL,11,Fvisits to Hong Kong, Vietnam and
OL,12,FSingapore with disgraced financier
OL,13,FEpstein.
OL,15,FHe has vehemently denied any
OL,16,Fwrongdoing over his Epstein links.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
