OL,3,CMan to appear in court after allegedly
OL,4,Cthreatening Andrew on Sandringham
OL,5,CEstate
OL,7,FAfter serving for 22 years in the
OL,8,FRoyal Navy, Andrew became the UK's
OL,9,Fspecial representative for
OL,10,Finternational trade and investment in
OL,11,F2001.
OL,13,FHe stepped down in 2011 amid the
OL,14,Ffurore over his friendship with
OL,15,Fpaedophile Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
